      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》周六报道，蒙佐下个月辞去这家英国移动银行首席执行官一职后，他将给予 TS Anil 更大的职位，向在他宣布离职后表示反对的顶级股东做出让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/monzo-give-outgoing-ceo-ts-anil-expanded-role-after-investor-backlash-ft-reports-2026-01-17/</guid>
