    <item>
      <title>MPS主要投资者卡尔塔吉龙表示与首席执行官洛瓦利奥没有冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/major-mps-investor-caltagirone-says-there-is-no-clash-with-ceo-lovaglio-2026-01-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Monte dei Paschi di Siena 的主要投资者卡尔塔吉龙集团 (Gruppo Caltagirone) 周五表示，关于与这家意大利银行首席执行官路易吉·洛瓦利奥 (Luigi Lovaglio) 发生冲突的猜测是错误的，并补充说董事会只是在讨论该银行的战略和治理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/major-mps-investor-caltagirone-says-there-is-no-clash-with-ceo-lovaglio-2026-01-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Jan 2026 14:57:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
